      "layout": "The page structure is full-bleed, allowing visual content to stretch across the viewport without a fixed max-width container, creating an immersive, gallery-like feel. The hero section often features oversized, overlapping typographic elements (Romie) that interact with the background imagery or serve as a dramatic overlay. Sections maintain consistent vertical spacing (80px), transitioning seamlessly rather than using distinct dividers. Content often appears as centered stacks, or large, unique visual compositions that imply a bespoke layout for each section rather than a strict grid.",
